title: Sirenia - Dim Days Of Dolor (Limited Edition) [2016]
description:
"Dim Days of Dolor" is the eighth full-length album by Norwegian gothic metal band Sirenia. It was released on November 11, 2016 through Napalm Records. It's their first album with vocalist Emmanuelle Zoldan.
